st Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/weekofyear"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeRef/weekOfYear":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"datetime"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(described below).","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"weekOfYear","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeref\/weekofyear","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeRef\/weekOfYear"},"doc://GLib/docu